 torque ±20%","testData":"","testResult":"","progressStatus":"대기중","reportStatus":"대기중","notes":"","photos":[],"graphs":[],"attachments":[],"id":"29f8d59f-dad1-48c6-98db-69cf457ecee6","lastModifiedDate":"2026-02-10"},{"projectId":"ea5a9192-67e9-42aa-9fb6-4a457308a029","name":"Torque performance : Step mode","plannedStartDate":"1/26/26","plannedEndDate":"2/2/26","actualEndDate":"2/2/26","testCondition":"1. Purpose:\r\n  To check the SFA step response for torque control\r\n2. Test set-up\r\n  a) Secure the SFA to a rigid fixture\r\n  b) Adjust the height and length adjustment to their mid positions\r\n  c) Power on\r\n  d) Connect input shaft to rigid fixture\r\n3. Test procedure\r\n  a) Apply feedback torque requests : 1.0, 3.0, 10.0Nm step\r\n  b) Repeat test for the opposite direction","judgmentCriteria":"1. T_10 : MAX 50ms\r\n2. T_90 : MAX 100ms\r\n3. Overshoot : Reference\r\n4. Static deviation : ±20%\r\n5. Settling time : MAX 300ms+J1","testData":"","testResult":"","progressStatus":"대기중","reportStatus":"대기중","notes":"","photos":[],"graphs":[],"attachments":[],"id":"43598b84-841b-4e0f-9fac-c231e32305a2","lastModifiedDate":"2026-02-10"},{"projectId":"ea5a9192-67e9-42aa-9fb6-4a457308a029","name":"Torque performance : Sweep mode","plannedStartDate":"1/31/26","plannedEndDate":"2/6/26","actualEndDate":"","testCondition":"1. Purpose\r\n  To check the SFA frequency response for torque control\r\n2.  Test set-up\r\n  a) Secure the SFA to a rigid fixture\r\n  b) Adjust the height and length adjustment to their mid positions\r\n  c) Power on\r\n  d) Connect input shaft to rigid fixture\r\n3. Test procedure\r\n  a) Apply feedback torque request \r\n   - Frequency : 0.5~25Hz (Log)\r\n   - Torque : 10~0.2Nm (Log)","judgmentCriteria":"1. MAX amplitude (0.5~5Hz) : 20%\r\n2. MAX amplitude (5Hz~) : Reference\r\n3. Phase shift (5Hz~) : Reference","testData":"","testResult":"","progressStatus":"대기중","reportStatus":"대기중","notes":"","photos":[],"graphs":[],"attachments":[],"id":"e9fb